[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "source": "self_notes_1",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "note",
    "text": "我做事习惯先把范围缩小，再开始动手。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 1
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "source": "self_notes_1",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "note",
    "text": "我不喜欢过度包装的表达，更希望信息密度高一点。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 2
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "source": "self_notes_1",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "note",
    "text": "如果一个想法还不够清楚，我通常不会急着下结论。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "source": "self_notes_1",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "note",
    "text": "我希望别人感受到我是冷静、具体、可靠，而不是热闹或者煽动。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 4
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "source": "self_notes_1",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "note",
    "text": "我写东西时会先列提纲，再补细节。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 5
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 1,
    "source": "self_notes_2",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "note",
    "text": "我倾向先做小范围验证，再决定要不要扩大。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 1
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "source": "self_notes_2",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "note",
    "text": "我不喜欢模糊表述，信息最好直接一点。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 2
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 1,
    "speaker": "我",
    "text": "先别急，我们先把问题定义清楚。",
    "source": "chat_sample_1",
    "kind": "chat",
    "meta": {
      "line": 1
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "speaker": "朋友",
    "text": "你说话一直都挺直接的，但不会让人觉得被顶着走。",
    "source": "chat_sample_1",
    "kind": "chat",
    "meta": {
      "line": 2
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "speaker": "我",
    "text": "对，我更在意把事情讲明白，而不是把气氛搞热。",
    "source": "chat_sample_1",
    "kind": "chat",
    "meta": {
      "line": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "speaker": "同事",
    "text": "你做决定前一般会先看有没有最小可行方案。",
    "source": "chat_sample_1",
    "kind": "chat",
    "meta": {
      "line": 4
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "speaker": "我",
    "text": "是，我通常先做一个能验证方向的小版本。",
    "source": "chat_sample_1",
    "kind": "chat",
    "meta": {
      "line": 5
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 1,
    "speaker": "我",
    "text": "这个先别铺太大，先看最小闭环。",
    "source": "chat_sample_2",
    "kind": "chat",
    "meta": {
      "line": 1
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "speaker": "同事",
    "text": "你一般会先收窄范围，再决定要不要扩。",
    "source": "chat_sample_2",
    "kind": "chat",
    "meta": {
      "line": 2
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 1,
    "source": "correction_round",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "correction",
    "text": "不像我：兄弟们冲、燃起来、绝了、情绪拉满。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 1
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "source": "correction_round",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "correction",
    "text": "更像我：先定义问题，再看怎么做；先讲清楚，再动手。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 2
    }
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "source": "correction_round",
    "speaker": "unknown",
    "kind": "correction",
    "text": "我不会这样说：这波太炸了，直接无脑上。",
    "meta": {
      "line": 3
    }
  }
]